=https://www.thedailystar.net/afsana-mimi-37128|title=AFSANA MIMI|date=2014-08-16|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2019-11-20}}</ref> She directed ''Kaacher Manush''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/bangla/anandadhara/%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%9B%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%9C%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%9F-%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A7%9C%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%A5%E0%A6%9A-%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%9C%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%9F-%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%AE%E0%A7%87-126262|title=\u2018\u09b8\u09ac\u0995\u09bf\u099b\u09c1\u09b0 \u09ac\u09be\u099c\u09c7\u099f \u09ac\u09be\u09a1\u09bc\u09c7 \u0985\u09a5\u099a \u09a8\u09be\u099f\u0995\u09c7\u09b0 \u09ac\u09be\u099c\u09c7\u099f \u0995\u09ae\u09c7\u2019|date=2019-11-19|website=The Daily Star Bangla|language=bn|access-date=2019-11-20}}</ref> She worked on a cooking show on ATN News named ''Nostalgia''.<ref name=mimi/>\n\nMimi serves as the director of ''Ichchhetola'', a cultural centre in Dhaka.<ref name=tola/>Lately she anchored a talk-show ''Moner Kotha''. She owns a production house named \"Krishnachura<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/magazine/2010/09/01/cover.htm|title=::: Star Weekend Magazine :::|website=www.thedailystar.net|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\".\n[[File:Afsanamimi.jpg|alt=|thumb|325x325px|Afsana Mimi Young]]\n<gallery widths=\"200\" heights=\"200\">\nFile:Afsanamimi kothao keu nei.jpg|kishor tarokaloke rokashito afsana mimi and shila ahmed (''[[Kothao Keu Nei]]'')\nFile:Afsanamimi Dil.jpg|Afsana mimi in Dil Movie\nFile:Afsanamimi Advertisement.jpg|advertisement in early 90s\nFile:Afsanamimi Advertisement young.jpg|Advertisements\nFile:Afsanamimi chitra nodir pare.jpg|Afsana mimi in ''[[Chitra Nodir Pare]]'' Movie\nFile:Afsanakarimmimi.jpg\n</gallery>\n\n\n== Works ==\n===Films===\n;Acting\n* ''[[Nodir Naam Modhumoti]]'' (1996)\n* ''[[Chitra Nodir Pare]]'' / Quiet Flows the River Chitra(1999)\n* ''Priyotomeshu'' (2009)\n*Bihango\n*Liliputra Boro Hobe\n*Chana o Muktijuddho\n*Dil (commercial film)\n\n=== Television ===\n;Acting\n\n*\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|'''Year'''\n|'''TV series and TV films'''\n|'''Director & Playwright'''\n|'''Co-stars'''\n|'''Notes'''\n|-\n|1990\n|''[[Kothao Keu Nei]]'' [[Kothao Keu Nei|(1990)]]<ref>{{cite news|author=Mohammad Zahidul Islam|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/afsana-mimi-37128|title=Afsana Mimi|date=August 16, 2014|newspaper=The Daily Star|accessdate=October 17, 2015}}</ref>\n|Humayun Ahmed\n|Suborna  Mustafa, Humayun Faridi, Abul Hayat\n|Drama  serial, aired on BTV\n|-\n|\n|Nokkhotrer Raat\n|Humayun Ahmed\n|Abul Khayer, Abul Hayat, Dilara Zaman, Aly Zaker, Sara Zaker, \nAsaduzzaman Noor, Dr. Enamul Haque, Lucky Enam, Abdul Quader, \n\nAzizul Hakim, Jahid Hasan, Meher Afroz Shaon, Shila Ahmed, Bipasha Ahmed,\n\nShomi Kaiser, Afsana Mimi, Saleh Uddin Ahmed, \n|Drama  serial, aired on BTV\n|-\n|\n|Kotha  Dilam\n|\n|Tony  Dayes\n|2nd  part \"Shei Tumi\"\n|-\n|\n|Sabuj Sathi\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|\n|Bandhan\n|\n|Jahid  Hasan\n|\n|-\n|\n|Kakhano  Shomoy Ashe\n|\n|Tony  Dayes\n|\n|-\n|\n|Nila  Namer Meyeti\n|\n|Tony  Dayes\n|\n|-\n|\n|Jiban  Jemon\n|\n|Zahid  Hasan\n|\n|-\n|\n|Shei  Tumi\n|\n|Tony  Dayes\n|1st  Part \"Kotha Dilam\"\n|-\n|\n|Shesh  Chithir Pore\n|\n|Tony  Dayes\n|\n|-\n|\n|Bishshash\n|\n|Mamunur  Rashid, Ali Zaker\n|\n|-\n|\n|Sthir  Chitro\n|\n|Salahuddin  Lavlu\n|\n|-\n|\n|Ontoray\n|\n|Tony  Dayes\n|Serial  Natok\n|-\n|\n|Bedonar  Rong Neel\n|\n|Tony  Dayes, Tarin Ahmed\n|Drama  serial\n|-\n|\n|Jhinuk  Nirobe Soho\n|\n|Tony  Dayes\n|Drama  serial\n|-\n|\n|Proshne  Tumi\n|\n|Tauquir  Ahmed\n|\n|-\n|\n|Sudhui  Tomare Jani\n|\n|Asaduzzaman  Noor\n|Drama  serial\n|-\n|\n|Mrittur  Opare\n|\n|Asaduzzaman  Noor\n|\n|-\n|\n|Amaro  Porano Jaha Chay\n|\n|Zahid  Hasan\n|\n|-\n|\n|Kusum  Kahini\n|\n|Zahid  Hasan\n|\n|-\n|\n|Badhon\n|\n|Zahid  Hasan\n|\n|-\n|1995\n|Nater  Guru\n|\n|Zahid  Hasan\n|\n|-\n|1992\n|Bou  Kotha Kow\n|\n|Asaduzzaman  Noor\n|\n|-\n|\n|Nayikar  Naame Naam\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|2005\n|Offbeat\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|2009\n|Ebong  Bonolota Sen\n|Tanvir  Hossain Probal\n|\n|\n|}\n\n*\n\n;Director\n\n* \n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|Year\n|TV series and TV films\n|Playwright\n|Artists\n|Notes\n|-\n|2001\n|Bandhan<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/news-detail-88788|title=Afsana Mimi talks direction and TV plays|date=2009-05-19|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|debut as director\n|-\n|\n|Share  Tin Tola\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|\n|Griho  Golpo\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|2006\n|Kaacher  Manush\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|2007\n|''[[Doll's House (TV series)|Doll's House]]'' [[Doll's House (TV series)|(2007-2009)]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/news/afsana-mimis-directorial-venture-shajal-after-decade-1764034|title=Afsana Mimi\u2019s directorial venture with Shajal after a decade|date=2019-06-29|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2019-11-20}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|Drama serial\n|-\n|2012\n|''Poush Phaguner Pala'' (2012)<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.priyo.com/entertainment/2012/03/14/poush-faguner-pala-tonight-atn-48175.html|title=\u2018Poush Faguner Pala\u2019 tonight on ATN Bangla|date=March 14, 2012|newspaper=Priyo News|accessdate=October 17, 2015|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122122414/http://news.priyo.com/entertainment/2012/03/14/poush-faguner-pala-tonight-atn-48175.html|archive-date=January 22, 2016|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|Gajendra  Kumar Mitra\n|Ferdousi  Majumdar, Humayun Faridi, Zahid Hasan\n|mega serial, adaptation novel trilogy of  Gajendra Kumar Mitra - \"Kolkata-r Kachhei\", \"Upokanthey\"  and \"Poush Faguner Pala\", aired on ATN Bangla\n|-\n|\n|''Bonhi''<ref name=\"projects\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/arts-entertainment/news/afsana-mimis-latest-projects-1768933|title=Afsana Mimi\u2019s latest projects|date=2019-07-10|website=The Daily Star|language=en|access-date=2019-11-20}}</ref>\n|